title: Birkin & Bubbles
description:
Casey and Danielle are as delighted to be joined by Ugly Betty’s Mark Indelicato as the gals were at the Birkin and Bubbles party. There’s trouble afoot in a disgusting mansion in Arizona for our Salt Lake gals and tensions boileth over between Rinna and Hilton in a glorious preview for the Reunion. We can only thank our lucky stars we get to witness this miracle!!!! Praise Be! 
 

It's the 6th Annual Bitch Sesh Live (from home) Halloween Spooktacular with special guest ANDY COHEN Thursday November 3rd at 5:30pm PST/ 8:30pm EST tickets https://app.loopedlive.com/c/3883 come dressed as in your favorite Bravo Cos-play there will be prizes awarded!!!
